### **IMAP Commands**

|Command|Description|
|---|---|
|LOGIN username password|Login|
|LIST "" *|List all directories|
|CREATE "INBOX"|Create mailbox|
|DELETE "INBOX"|Delete mailbox|
|RENAME "ToRead" "Important"|Rename mailbox|
|LSUB "" *|List subscribed mailboxes|
|SELECT INBOX|Access mailbox|
|UNSELECT INBOX|Exit mailbox|
|FETCH <ID> all|Retrieve message data|
|CLOSE|Remove messages marked deleted|
|LOGOUT|Close server connection|

### **POP3 Commands**

|Command|Description|
|---|---|
|USER username|Identify user|
|PASS password|Authenticate user|
|STAT|Number of emails on server|
|LIST|Number and size of all emails|
|RETR id|Retrieve email by ID|
|DELE id|Delete email by ID|
|CAPA|Server capabilities|
|RSET|Reset transmitted info|
|QUIT|Close server connection|

